600 m greenland inverse problem / stage 1 / 31 Oct 2025

purpose
-------

Refine the initial guess (btrc = rho*g*h*grad(s)/u) with m = 1
to avoid poor perfomance with (e.g) m = 1/3.  

job
---
run on tuna


